title: ETH v1 Update: Collateral Factor and Collateral Cap - Mass Update
body:
Intro: This is a vote to update the collateral factors and collateral caps on the ETH v1 C.R.E.A.M. market.

Proposal: Listing Committee 

Rational: Update and improve ETH v1 market.

For:
Update Collateral Factors and Collateral Caps EXACTLY as displayed in sheets — https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1F-7RcY7OtE6tLSRq5fUMK2bnI0MSO-6zfNLV1CKiEUU/edit?usp=sharing

Against:
Do not make any changes to ETH v1 market.
author: 0x81f8CaBe89066d43EB4faFD8E4E5256C102E6E30
